features: 『High-quality Material』Kitchen pantry storage cabinet adopts large-sized thickened cold-rolled steel plate and electrostatic powder spraying technology. After special treatment, each layer can withstand up to 180 pounds of weight, with sufficient hardness and durability

『Flexible Storage』There are 3 adjustable height shelves in the kitchen pantry, which can be disassembled or adjusted according to your needs, greatly improving applicability and flexibility to meet your unique storage and sorting needs

『EASY Assembly』61.02" H×27.55"W×13.78"D. Two wing doors designed to mimic the style of wooden cabinet doors, with an opening angle of 180 °. The metal storage cabinet kitchen is a detachable structure with installation videos and instructions for easy assembly. Suggest two adults gather together

『Other Design』There are 2 reserved holes on the back of the kitchen pantry cabinet to facilitate installation on the wall and prevent overturning. 4 detachable leveling feet, which can maintain cabinet stability while moisture-proof and facilitate cleaning

『Multi Purpose』The storage cabinet with doors and shelves are suitable for various home and office spaces, such as kid's rooms, kitchens, restaurants, bedrooms, study rooms, living rooms, entrances, etc. The GAIOUS team will resolve your issue within 24 hours

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love it! Great service!
reviews.reviewText: The Pantry was delivered promptly and arrived intact, without any damage, and all the components were included. Following the easily understandable instructions, assembly took approximately an hour.Once fully assembled, this cabinet truly showcases its beauty, and my husband managed to put it together within just a couple of hours.I had concerns about potential odors, as many furniture items tend to have unpleasant smells, but I'm pleased to report that this cabinet is entirely odor-free. My choice has proven to be a wise one.During its use, I encountered a minor query, and the customer care representative who assisted me demonstrated an exceptional ability to resolve issues, displayed professionalism, and followed up diligently.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I eagerly anticipated the arrival of this cabinet for a span of six days, and I must admit my excitement upon its delivery. My spouse shares in my enthusiasm for this new addition to our home.As has been previously noted by others, the assembly instructions are straightforward to follow. Given my proficiency in assembly, my wife and I managed to put it together in a mere 35 minutes. However, for those lacking assembly experience, the process might be a bit more time-consuming. Nevertheless, it's worth mentioning that the cabinet boasts a simple structure, making it suitable for beginners as well.The storage capacity of this cabinet is truly impressive, and it is entirely devoid of any unpleasant odors, which we find quite pleasing.It's important to mention that the protective film on the acrylic glass panel requires removal. Initially, we overlooked the fact that one of the acrylic glass panels had a protective film that was tightly affixed, resulting in a mismatched color with the other three panels after assembly. Fortunately, I contacted a customer service representative who promptly and effectively assisted us in investigating and resolving this issue, for which we commend their excellent service.This cabinet is undeniably beautiful, and we are already considering purchasing more for our kitchen and bathroom.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I am very happy with my purchase and it looks beautiful in my dining room. This cabinet wasn’t that hard to put together but I def recommend 2 people assisting in assembly. reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy and attractive
reviews.reviewText: First thing to know that I didn't really realize before buying was this is 100% metal, even the doors. That said it's very attractive, and the doors you have to really get up on it too realize their metal because they look like furniture, especially with the handles. I needed a storage cabinet for my finished basement and this was perfect. Very solid and can hold heavy things. It's about 5 feet tall. I would buy again.
